@node neuf

Good question

1°) IFF-packing IFF (680x0) and the drawing (68020+) have been optimized.

2°) Argument -nc disable IFF packing. Usefull when there's a lack of memory.

3°) FracPro runs under NTSC.

4°) Awfull bug removed.

5°) CycleToMenu compatible.

@endnode

