@node Intro "Introduction"

FracPro is another Fractals drawer program. It was written at first for
@{"fun" link Copyright}, and to see if it can be as fast as its opponents.

FracPro is the highly improved version of Mandel.... (DPAT #49).

FracPro applys to those who want use fractals pictures in raytracing.
Pictures are virtualy written in memory in 24 bits, but displayed in 1bit !!


Advantages follows :

	- The size of the picture is only limited by the amount of memory.

	- Pictures are very precise. They can be used in mapping.

	- Computation isn't slowed by displaying.


FracPro makes use of a special mode '@{"Oil-Paint" link rendu}' that create the most
beautiful picture I've ever seend.

@endnode

@node Compatibilite "Compatibility"

FracPro needs at least KickStart 2.0

FracPro needs at least 1Mo and @{"Reqtools.library" link merci} in drawer LIBS:
68000'version will need MathTrans.library and FPU versions the
MathIEEEDoubTrans.library

FracPro will use improved graphics routines if you're under Kickstart 3.0


Warning !
---------

For confortable using, you should have a FPU and FAST memory.

@endnode

